dev.nokee.platform.objectivec

Interface ObjectiveCApplicationExtension

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryAwareComponent, Component, DependencyAwareComponent<NativeApplicationComponentDependencies>, HasObjectiveCSources, HasPrivateHeaders, SourceAwareComponent<ObjectiveCApplicationSources>, TargetBuildTypeAwareComponent, TargetMachineAwareComponent, VariantAwareComponent<NativeApplication>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ObjectiveCApplication
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface ObjectiveCApplicationExtension
extends DependencyAwareComponent<NativeApplicationComponentDependencies>, VariantAwareComponent<NativeApplication>, BinaryAwareComponent, TargetMachineAwareComponent, TargetBuildTypeAwareComponent, SourceAwareComponent<ObjectiveCApplicationSources>, HasPrivateHeaders, HasObjectiveCSources
    Configuration for an application written in Objective-C, defining the dependencies that make up the application plus other settings.

    An instance of this type is added as a project extension by the Objective-C Application Plugin.

    0.4
